cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and semantic parsing. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves machine learning techniques for learning structured embeddings. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with understanding the meaning of text, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves training neural networks.
